name: Raw Chicken Experiment
description: $RCE, the meme coin inspired by John, the internet phenomenon who's taken the world by storm by eating raw chicken every day. With over 300,000 followers on Instagram and millions of views across his content, John's unique challenge has not only drawn attention but also sparked discussions everywhere, from the Daily Mail to Vice, and even making waves on Pubity. Now on day 46, John's journey isn't just about pushing dietary boundaries; it's become a symbol of internet virality and the unexpected paths to fame.
